headline: Can Pottery Barn’s Pop Culture Collaborations Deepen Williams-Sonoma’s Brand Affinity and Moat (WSM)?
summary: Pottery Barn, a portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc., recently announced exclusive collaborations, including a Norman Rockwell holiday home decor collection and a multi-brand partnership inspired by Universal’s Wicked film, expanding its seasonal and fan-driven product offerings.
